  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mini Star Math: 4 Routes is a math memorization challenge game with 13 stages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A.1 coin classic mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rules of this game are simple. If you lose all your health, it's game over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve tons of math problems to reach the end of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/383b2f32053b6ef5743e6b1060dbeebb.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/383b2f32053b6ef5743e6b1060dbeebb.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/383b2f32053b6ef5743e6b1060dbeebb.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B. Route System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can choose which formulas will appear in the next stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/91b71160dc55afcf5b80dc4b4c03ac42.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/91b71160dc55afcf5b80dc4b4c03ac42.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/91b71160dc55afcf5b80dc4b4c03ac42.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >C. Shop System</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every time you solve a problem correctly, you will earn coins, which can be used to purchase useful items in various kinds of shops that appear after you clear a stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/9ee9659f3445ccc5cfdc0923ac7c7e93.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/9ee9659f3445ccc5cfdc0923ac7c7e93.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/9ee9659f3445ccc5cfdc0923ac7c7e93.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >D. Practice mode support</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports practice mode, where you can freely practice 32 formulas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/31623eb7bd569397294c4ce330647970.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/31623eb7bd569397294c4ce330647970.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/31623eb7bd569397294c4ce330647970.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >E. Support 3 difficulty levels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/6901fc35c2e092699a5e2916c2c7c647.poster.avif?t=1732845435\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/6901fc35c2e092699a5e2916c2c7c647.webm?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313810/extras/6901fc35c2e092699a5e2916c2c7c647.mp4?t=1732845435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
